  <div id="text-content_7c28f669-4774-4619-8f45-32f848287b5a" class="text-block-content">
    <p>After adding a hyperlink to <a href="/t5/Instructor-Guide/How-do-I-create-hyperlinks-to-external-URLs-in-the-Rich-Content/ta-p/872" target="_blank">external URLs,</a> <a href="/t5/Instructor-Guide/How-do-I-create-hyperlinks-to-course-or-group-content-in-the/ta-p/954" target="_blank">course content</a>, or <a href="/t5/Instructor-Guide/How-do-I-create-hyperlinks-to-course-group-and-user-files-in-the/ta-p/959" target="_blank">files</a> in the Rich Content Editor, you can edit the link from the Link Options menu. You can also remove hyperlinks.</p>
  </div>
</div>

    <div class="html-embed">
  <iframe width="560px" height="320px" allowfullscreen="true" allow="autoplay *" title="Canvas Shorts: How do I edit and remove hyperlinks in the Rich Content Editor?" src="https://community.instructuremedia.com/embed/ee18bfb2-9027-47e6-8c62-ce9c2288b3ba" frameborder="0"></iframe>
</div>


      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="open_rich_content_editor" data-step-uuid="92f2c543-c3fa-41c7-9c68-00553e001a61">
    <h2 id="open_rich_content_editor" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Open Rich Content Editor</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <a href="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/008/393/863/original/97874299-0555-496f-91d1-13a68cab3ae3.png" class="screensteps-image-zoom" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer">
        <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/008/393/863/medium/97874299-0555-496f-91d1-13a68cab3ae3.png" srcset="" alt="Open Rich Content Editor" height="340" width="855">
      </a>
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_d6563f96-e131-4d65-b769-f2de4feafbfc" class="text-block-content">
    <p>Open the Rich Content Editor to create or edit an announcement, assignment, discussion, page, quiz, or syllabus.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="edit-link" data-step-uuid="41f1873c-5ef8-436f-936e-02a0c45a8f41">
    <h2 id="edit-link" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Edit Link</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/004/851/100/original/ea7c94f2-740a-4aa0-8606-39a15adb5ecc.png" srcset="" alt="Edit Link" height="358" width="795">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_0b4f4a0c-6da8-47b5-9724-4c9ee6f17cc9" class="text-block-content">
    <p>Click the link in the Rich Content Editor [1]. Then click the <strong>Link Options</strong> link [2]. </p>
<p>You can also click the <strong>Link Options </strong>arrow [3] and select the <strong>Edit Link </strong>option [4].</p>
<p><strong>Note:</strong> To view the Links icon, you may have to click the <strong>Options</strong> icon [5]. Â </p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="view-link-options" data-step-uuid="8e433119-5f16-48be-a881-e800c4503c02">
    <h2 id="view-link-options" class="step-title screensteps-heading">View Link Options</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/002/866/545/original/4b4f06e3-313f-465d-8373-3ebb72dba854.png" srcset="" alt="View Link Options" height="419" width="323">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_e7b0003a-fbc6-4f34-bb54-09427a0a75a2" class="text-block-content">
    <p>In the Link Options menu, you can edit the hyperlinked text in the <strong>Text </strong>field [1]. You can edit the URL in the <strong>Link</strong> field [2]. </p>
<p>To save your changes, click the <strong>Done </strong>button [3]. </p>
<p><strong>Note: </strong>When clicked, external hyperlinks automatically open in a new browser tab.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="remove-link" data-step-uuid="823ce339-4d4d-48b2-802a-cc79e3740dab">
    <h2 id="remove-link" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Remove Link</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/004/851/103/original/900cf937-e972-4b4d-9702-46546042a23b.png" srcset="" alt="Remove Link" height="358" width="795">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_3a13f4d3-d48d-4805-8f53-f59b55df19af" class="text-block-content">
    <p>To remove a link, click the <strong>Link Options</strong> arrow [1] and select the <strong>Remove Link </strong>option [2]. </p>
  </div>
</div>
 
        <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-2" id="remove-multiple-links" data-step-uuid="8f219fa9-c31d-461c-8c03-3a2963f2c861">
    <h3 id="remove-multiple-links" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Remove Multiple Links</h3>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/004/851/105/original/f2f57d91-1730-4d81-9d13-d0276e2dab16.png" srcset="" alt="Remove Multiple Links" height="377" width="795">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_c4259012-0a20-460f-b610-3ca0bb7c4bbd" class="text-block-content">
    <p>To remove multiple links, highlight the text that contains the links you want to remove [1]. Then click the <strong>Link Options</strong> arrow [2] and select the <strong>Remove Links </strong>option [3].</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>
 
        <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-2" id="save-changes" data-step-uuid="050f865d-a640-49c7-9c96-2718ae36a628">
    <h3 id="save-changes" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Save Changes</h3>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/002/878/350/original/e90bc4e6-9856-452a-8328-27048ba4dbb3.png" srcset="" alt="Save Changes" height="68" width="172">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_8c6396d0-cca0-4d2e-8232-bad3a9322325" class="text-block-content">
    <p>Click the <strong>Save</strong> button.</p>
<p><strong>Notes: </strong></p>
<ul>
<li>The assignment, discussion, pages, and quizzes details pages display a <strong>Save &amp; Publish</strong> button. </li>
<li>The Syllabus page displays an <strong>Update Syllabus</strong> button. </li>
<li>Discussion replies display a <strong>Post Reply</strong> button.</li>
</ul>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>
 
  </div>
					
				
			
			
			
				
			
			
			
			
			
			
